Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:48.90,kakeru,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru Okikura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:12.38,toko,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Touko Fukami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:15.88,yukinari,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinari Imi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:15.88,hiro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro Shirosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.85,kakeru,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi Takayama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:35.24,sachi,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sachi Nagamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:00.84,Episode-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(531,679)}Episode 1\N"Fireworks"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:02.97,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.99,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.87,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I take everything seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.46,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.98,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.94,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these things have \Ngotten really advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.40,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,They were so crummy when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:33.79,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.72,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.87,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can take it \Nback to Sacchan as a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.39,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,A bit much, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.04,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.02,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Like, I have—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.73,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, don't drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.63,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me. I have good reflexes, Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,but you're paying for it if you break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.84,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,After all I went through to make \Nsure we can split it completely evenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.69,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I used to come here every day during \Nmy high school entrance exam days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.39,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't this pretty far from your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,This kid gets pumped only when he's running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He could run forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.00,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "only"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last year we're \Nall meeting up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:48.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.64,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why so negative?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.81,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We could all come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.16,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, next year, and the year after...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.98,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be friends forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.27,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Forever? Who knows what'll \Nhappen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.48,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:06.07,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to stop being \Nfriends once we graduate? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.14,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,there's no telling what might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.79,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,They say that if you say \Nyour wishes out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,you'll end up granting them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:19.20,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe instead of saying "we won't come here," \Nwe should say "let's come again."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.64,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get that from Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.30,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.88,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is that no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.56,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,my future self will fix it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.92,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.98,Main,Cus1,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.71,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Two iced coffees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.55,Main,Cus2,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.45,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Yukkii, give me a hand please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.26,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.75,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Since when is he "Yukkii"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.72,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,They're totally best buds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.98,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,More toast for the iced coffee customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.76,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Such a salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:05.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa's so nice to Yukinari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.59,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can hardly tell who's the grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.70,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-kun's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.47,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,With the elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.37,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:15.97,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What about Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.23,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so delicious when you eat out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to stay away from ramune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.42,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks to be watching your weight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.21,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.22,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.77,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks were so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.34,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Like, boom, bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.34,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,The festival's ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.09,bridge,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinode\N Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.40,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.34,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:21.37,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.04,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.59,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.10,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.95,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hot, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.38,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What should I make?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.73,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,This again, Mom? \NWhy do even bother asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.90,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.81,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a sec. \NHina, what do you want for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.26,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I saw some cabbage left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.39,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.12,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,See, all three of us have the same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.23,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't bring mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.74,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are tactful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.22,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That thing on the door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.12,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You could have brought it if you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.02,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You make a fuss whenever I touch \Nyour stuff without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.81,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you went in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:35.26,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it again that asked me to bring \Nthe reference book you left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.61,exile,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Exile and the Kingdom\NCamus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.84,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.00,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,David.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.51,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,David?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.26,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.93,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, I thought you'd left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.98,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure your parents see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.52,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:05.18,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pain, transferring schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.34,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,What year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:06.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.91,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.27,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds tough, transferring in your third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.06,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:12.71,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:13.96,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.46,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Touko Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.17,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.59,Italics,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,He's calling me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.37,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you at fireworks the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.18,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You were buying a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:32.93,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.74,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,That's the chicken's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.11,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's Husserl, Confucius,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.83,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, and Makuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:43.02,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,We're all taking care of them at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.82,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,but I think the ethics \Nteacher puts in the most time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.87,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan's from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why it's not fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.17,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,They're free-range, so they're so hard to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You could just put them in a coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.82,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.12,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.19,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't Jonathan running away? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.30,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.64,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if they get to \Ngo wherever they want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.02,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your own point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.01,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.64,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.48,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,there aren't any animals that'd \Ngo into cages on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.40,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's because they don't \Nhave enough options.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:28.16,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,This is a port town. \NThere are lots of cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.91,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Ever considered that they \Nmight get attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.00,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,They're all full from eating fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.08,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.17,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard about any of \Nthem getting attacked by cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.13,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What about other than cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.18,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan can fly awa—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.38,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.59,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.24,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they could fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.90,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I friend or foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.41,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll protect Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.55,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Please and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.81,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.13,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.76,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How did I get dragged into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.35,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.54,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain in detail tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.44,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yana-chan okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.40,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. She's not completely heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.73,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Momo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.82,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.15,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She just got her license.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She can't wait to drive someone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.75,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Tee hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. I never signed up for this, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.35,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why'd you put it in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.65,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I texted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.20,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It might get attacked if it's outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.98,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the two of them in your room, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.89,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,And I told you I can't check \Nmy messages during lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:42.64,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mean. They aren't \Nin their familiar environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.09,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:48.44,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,you should learn how to count chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.49,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is another favor for Touko, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:55.43,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You always do everything Touko asks you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.10,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.40,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had ramune in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.32,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.73,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do it yourself. Learn from Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.83,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:15.77,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.95,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,always wanted chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.45,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,if Touko told you to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.39,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.92,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,She... wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.30,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I know she wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's have hot pot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.51,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hot pot in the summer. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.87,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.99,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,are you happy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.74,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,How do you want to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:33.05,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Am I keeping you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.15,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.75,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.33,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,It's mid-summer. Why chicken hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.90,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Have you considered how hot it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.38,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a craving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.76,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:07.23,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.09,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.15,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you just randomly \Nbring home a chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.68,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.24,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, It was just impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.54,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.75,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I got everyone involved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.43,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't even solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.83,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no difference between putting \Nhim in a room and putting him in a coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.96,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,What does Jonathan even think of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.65,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I guess I fooled myself into
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.99,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,thinking I knew what Jonathan wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.41,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We got some good chicken today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:40.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:50.89,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of chicken, I remember \Nmy first date with Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.94,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.09,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It was our first date, and he was {\i1}late{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:58.38,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You were the late one. Two hours late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:02.60,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I asked you if you waited, \Nand you said "I just got here."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.12,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.99,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,So what does that have \Nto do with chickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:09.74,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I got caught up copying a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.45,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Jakuchuu chicken painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.56,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you paint a chicken \Nbefore your first date?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.23,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there more important things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.60,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.98,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're so naive, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:25.24,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,So you're less interested in \NDad than you are in chickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:26.89,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.06,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go somewhere Sachi \Ncan go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:42.89,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.03,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,We went hiking together \Nlast year, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.37,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.35,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.80,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let the festival end just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.20,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.99,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit late to get \Nready now, so, tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.02,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.36,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never taking care of chickens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.61,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Never, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:06.88,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:07.75,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.11,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,They were cute, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.87,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,A giant tanuki might have gotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,them if we hadn't taken them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where the heck do \Ngiant tanuki even live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Touché.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.29,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Yuki let them in \Nmy room in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.91,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you don't even \Nknow how to count them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.14,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:24.70,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.62,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Chickens really do crow in the morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.77,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't lay any eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:39.43,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if zoo animals are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.15,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,what made you decide to take them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.34,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... A transfer student...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.93,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,He's a third year, and looks like David...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:02.62,Italics,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.36,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:07.45,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, his name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.41,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,David Okikura?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.25,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was doing the \Nright thing for Jonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.10,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:27.12,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I figured there'd be guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.23,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:46.73,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,what you saw that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.93,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll ask him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:33.39,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't pull anything weird, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.24,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:34.89,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.85,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.03,Main,Toko,0000,0000,0000,,Be open to love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.35,Episode-Title - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2\N"Bench"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.35,Episode-Title - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,
